articles.title: Business in the front, party in the back: Tennessee woman has longest competitive mullet - Guinness World Records
articles.description: The world’s longest competitive mullet (female) measures 172.72 cm (5 ft 8 in) and sits on the head of 58-year-old Tami Manis from Knoxville, Tennessee.
articles.content:
